{{Quote|A dead dragon—a [[dracolich]]—wishes the love of a [[half-elf]]?|[[Ruha]], astounded by the plot unfolding before her.}}
During the mid–14{{th}} century [[DR]], Minister [[Hsieh Han Liu]] of the [[Ginger Palace]] dealt in ylang blossoms, importing them to the [[Eastern Heartlands]] from Shou Lung via his ship, the ''[[Ginger Lady]]''.

In the {{YearlinkName|1364}}, the dracolich [[Hethcypressarvil]] schemed to use oil made from the ylang blossoms imported to the Ginger Palace to creature a ''love potion'' that would force [[Yanseldara]] of [[Elversult]] to love him.
